{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1062,"text":"Good morning."},{"time":3327,"text":"When I was a little boy,"},{"time":5114,"text":"I had an experience that changed my life,"},{"time":8191,"text":"and is in fact why I'm here today."},{"time":11099,"text":"That one moment"},{"time":13040,"text":"profoundly affected how I think about"},{"time":15302,"text":"art, design and engineering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18523,"text":"As background, I was fortunate enough to grow up"},{"time":21280,"text":"in a family of loving and talented artists"},{"time":24993,"text":"in one of the world's great cities."},{"time":27557,"text":"My dad, John Ferren, who died when I was 15,"},{"time":31434,"text":"was an artist by both passion and profession,"},{"time":34964,"text":"as is my mom, Rae."},{"time":37224,"text":"He was one of the New York School"},{"time":39029,"text":"abstract expressionists who,"},{"time":40790,"text":"together with his contemporaries,"},{"time":43302,"text":"invented American modern art,"},{"time":46200,"text":"and contributed to moving the American zeitgeist"},{"time":49385,"text":"towards modernism in the 20th century."},{"time":53928,"text":"Isn't it remarkable that, after thousands of years"},{"time":56849,"text":"of people doing mostly representational art,"},{"time":60490,"text":"that modern art, comparatively speaking,"},{"time":62523,"text":"is about 15 minutes old,"},{"time":64863,"text":"yet now pervasive."},{"time":66761,"text":"As with many other important innovations,"},{"time":68705,"text":"those radical ideas required no new technology,"},{"time":72325,"text":"just fresh thinking and a willingness to experiment,"},{"time":75218,"text":"plus resiliency in the face of near-universal criticism"},{"time":79386,"text":"and rejection."},{"time":80840,"text":"In our home, art was everywhere."},{"time":83357,"text":"It was like oxygen,"},{"time":84928,"text":"around us and necessary for life."},{"time":88090,"text":"As I watched him paint,"},{"time":89949,"text":"Dad taught me that art"},{"time":92256,"text":"was not about being decorative,"},{"time":94465,"text":"but was a different way of communicating ideas,"},{"time":97579,"text":"and in fact one that could bridge the worlds"},{"time":99616,"text":"of knowledge and insight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102544,"text":"Given this rich artistic environment,"},{"time":104684,"text":"you'd assume that I would have been compelled"},{"time":106299,"text":"to go into the family business,"},{"time":108408,"text":"but no."},{"time":111024,"text":"I followed the path of most kids"},{"time":112811,"text":"who are genetically programmed"},{"time":114161,"text":"to make their parents crazy."},{"time":116360,"text":"I had no interest in becoming an artist,"},{"time":118983,"text":"certainly not a painter."},{"time":120543,"text":"What I did love was electronics and machines --"},{"time":123842,"text":"taking them apart, building new ones,"},{"time":125462,"text":"and making them work."},{"time":127349,"text":"Fortunately, my family also had engineers in it,"},{"time":131251,"text":"and with my parents,"},{"time":132459,"text":"these were my first role models."},{"time":135087,"text":"What they all had in common"},{"time":136444,"text":"was they worked very, very hard."},{"time":139152,"text":"My grandpa owned and operated a sheet metal"},{"time":141522,"text":"kitchen cabinet factory in Brooklyn."},{"time":144222,"text":"On weekends, we would go\ntogether to Cortlandt Street,"},{"time":147646,"text":"which was New York City's radio row."},{"time":150321,"text":"There we would explore massive piles"},{"time":153124,"text":"of surplus electronics,"},{"time":154345,"text":"and for a few bucks bring home treasures"},{"time":156647,"text":"like Norden bombsights"},{"time":158079,"text":"and parts from the first IBM tube-based computers."},{"time":162590,"text":"I found these objects both useful and fascinating."},{"time":165656,"text":"I learned about engineering and how things worked,"},{"time":168287,"text":"not at school"},{"time":169747,"text":"but by taking apart and studying"},{"time":171536,"text":"these fabulously complex devices."},{"time":174013,"text":"I did this for hours every day,"},{"time":176597,"text":"apparently avoiding electrocution."},{"time":179895,"text":"Life was good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181467,"text":"However, every summer, sadly,"},{"time":183788,"text":"the machines got left behind"},{"time":185821,"text":"while my parents and I traveled overseas"},{"time":188025,"text":"to experience history, art and design."},{"time":191665,"text":"We visited the great museums and historic buildings"},{"time":194059,"text":"of both Europe and the Middle East,"},{"time":195919,"text":"but to encourage my growing interest"},{"time":198179,"text":"in science and technology,"},{"time":199994,"text":"they would simply drop me off in places"},{"time":202278,"text":"like the London Science Museum,"},{"time":204718,"text":"where I would wander endlessly for hours by myself"},{"time":208436,"text":"studying the history of science and technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212412,"text":"Then, when I was about nine years old,"},{"time":215676,"text":"we went to Rome."},{"time":217544,"text":"On one particularly hot summer day,"},{"time":219905,"text":"we visited a drum-shaped\nbuilding that from the outside"},{"time":222784,"text":"was not particularly interesting."},{"time":225028,"text":"My dad said it was called the Pantheon,"},{"time":227353,"text":"a temple for all of the gods."},{"time":229821,"text":"It didn't look all that special from the outside,"},{"time":232095,"text":"as I said, but when we walked inside,"},{"time":234534,"text":"I was immediately struck by three things:"},{"time":237847,"text":"First of all, it was pleasantly cool"},{"time":241077,"text":"despite the oppressive heat outside."},{"time":243155,"text":"It was very dark, the only source of light"},{"time":245869,"text":"being an big open hole in the roof."},{"time":248342,"text":"Dad explained that this wasn't a big open hole,"},{"time":250575,"text":"but it was called the oculus,"},{"time":252389,"text":"an eye to the heavens."},{"time":254765,"text":"And there was something about this place,"},{"time":256910,"text":"I didn't know why, that just felt special."},{"time":259913,"text":"As we walked to the center of the room,"},{"time":261911,"text":"I looked up at the heavens through the oculus."},{"time":264732,"text":"This was the first church that I'd been to"},{"time":267029,"text":"that provided an unrestricted view"},{"time":269232,"text":"between God and man."},{"time":272390,"text":"But I wondered, what about when it rained?"},{"time":275820,"text":"Dad may have called this an oculus,"},{"time":277677,"text":"but it was, in fact, a big hole in the roof."},{"time":280764,"text":"I looked down and saw floor drains"},{"time":282593,"text":"had been cut into the stone floor."},{"time":285178,"text":"As I became more accustomed to the dark,"},{"time":287637,"text":"I was able to make out details of the floor"},{"time":289901,"text":"and the surrounding walls."},{"time":291631,"text":"No big deal here, just the same statuary stuff"},{"time":294208,"text":"that we'd seen all over Rome."},{"time":296124,"text":"In fact, it looked like the Appian Way"},{"time":297796,"text":"marble salesman showed up"},{"time":299992,"text":"with his sample book, showed it to Hadrian,"},{"time":302440,"text":"and Hadrian said, \"We'll take all of it.\""},{"time":305080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":306786,"text":"But the ceiling was amazing."},{"time":310004,"text":"It looked like a Buckminster Fuller geodesic dome."},{"time":312840,"text":"I'd seen these before,"},{"time":314149,"text":"and Bucky was friends with my dad."},{"time":316393,"text":"It was modern, high-tech, impressive,"},{"time":319884,"text":"a huge 142-foot clear span"},{"time":322321,"text":"which, not coincidentally, was exactly its height."},{"time":325564,"text":"I loved this place."},{"time":326826,"text":"It was really beautiful and unlike\nanything I'd ever seen before,"},{"time":330245,"text":"so I asked my dad, \"When was this built?\""},{"time":333815,"text":"He said, \"About 2,000 years ago.\""},{"time":336947,"text":"And I said, \"No, I mean, the roof.\""},{"time":339451,"text":"You see, I assumed that this was a modern roof"},{"time":341410,"text":"that had been put on because the original"},{"time":343328,"text":"was destroyed in some long-past war."},{"time":346874,"text":"He said, \"It's the original roof.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":350336,"text":"That moment changed my life,"},{"time":352814,"text":"and I can remember it as if it were yesterday."},{"time":355463,"text":"For the first time, I realized people were smart"},{"time":358058,"text":"2,000 years ago. (Laughter)"},{"time":360198,"text":"This had never crossed my mind."},{"time":362312,"text":"I mean, to me, the pyramids at Giza,"},{"time":366183,"text":"we visited those the year before,"},{"time":368111,"text":"and sure they're impressive, nice enough design,"},{"time":371031,"text":"but look, give me an unlimited budget,"},{"time":373486,"text":"20,000 to 40,000 laborers, and about 10 to 20 years"},{"time":377483,"text":"to cut and drag stone blocks \nacross the countryside,"},{"time":381099,"text":"and I'll build you pyramids too."},{"time":383863,"text":"But no amount of brute force"},{"time":386666,"text":"gets you the dome of the Pantheon,"},{"time":389708,"text":"not 2,000 years ago, nor today."},{"time":392727,"text":"And incidentally, it is still the largest"},{"time":395467,"text":"unreinforced concrete dome that's ever been built."},{"time":399281,"text":"To build the Pantheon took some miracles."},{"time":402276,"text":"By miracles, I mean things that are"},{"time":404708,"text":"technically barely possible,"},{"time":407295,"text":"very high-risk, and might not be"},{"time":410367,"text":"actually accomplishable at this moment in time,"},{"time":412951,"text":"certainly not by you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417203,"text":"For example, here are some\nof the Pantheon's miracles."},{"time":420328,"text":"To make it even structurally possible,"},{"time":423021,"text":"they had to invent super-strong concrete,"},{"time":425588,"text":"and to control weight,"},{"time":427537,"text":"varied the density of the aggregate"},{"time":429605,"text":"as they worked their way up the dome."},{"time":432373,"text":"For strength and lightness, the dome structure"},{"time":434674,"text":"used five rings of coffers,"},{"time":436711,"text":"each of diminishing size,"},{"time":438318,"text":"which imparts a dramatic forced perspective"},{"time":441054,"text":"to the design."},{"time":443061,"text":"It was wonderfully cool inside"},{"time":444986,"text":"because of its huge thermal mass,"},{"time":447169,"text":"natural convection of air rising up"},{"time":449254,"text":"through the oculus,"},{"time":450655,"text":"and a Venturi effect when wind blows across"},{"time":453130,"text":"the top of the building."},{"time":455433,"text":"I discovered for the first time that light itself"},{"time":459393,"text":"has substance."},{"time":461360,"text":"The shaft of light beaming through the oculus"},{"time":464037,"text":"was both beautiful and palpable,"},{"time":466527,"text":"and I realized for the first time"},{"time":468784,"text":"that light could be designed."},{"time":470685,"text":"Further, that of all of the forms of design,"},{"time":475559,"text":"visual design,"},{"time":476935,"text":"they were all kind of irrelevant without it,"},{"time":478766,"text":"because without light, you can't see any of them."},{"time":482627,"text":"I also realized that I wasn't the first person"},{"time":485079,"text":"to think that this place was really special."},{"time":488338,"text":"It survived gravity, barbarians, looters, developers"},{"time":492715,"text":"and the ravages of time to become"},{"time":494614,"text":"what I believe is the longest"},{"time":495994,"text":"continuously occupied building in history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498951,"text":"Largely because of that visit,"},{"time":501167,"text":"I came to understand that,"},{"time":502704,"text":"contrary to what I was being told in school,"},{"time":505343,"text":"the worlds of art and design"},{"time":507372,"text":"were not, in fact, incompatible"},{"time":509388,"text":"with science and engineering."},{"time":511064,"text":"I realized, when combined,"},{"time":513157,"text":"you could create things that were amazing"},{"time":515920,"text":"that couldn't be done in either domain alone."},{"time":518766,"text":"But in school, with few exceptions,"},{"time":521199,"text":"they were treated as separate worlds,"},{"time":523119,"text":"and they still are."},{"time":525262,"text":"My teachers told me that I had to get serious"},{"time":527958,"text":"and focus on one or the other."},{"time":530131,"text":"However, urging me to specialize"},{"time":533226,"text":"only caused me to really \nappreciate those polymaths"},{"time":536536,"text":"like Michelangelo, Leonardo da Vinci,"},{"time":540686,"text":"Benjamin Franklin,"},{"time":542111,"text":"people who did exactly the opposite."},{"time":544821,"text":"And this led me to embrace"},{"time":547010,"text":"and want to be in both worlds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549980,"text":"So then how do these projects of unprecedented creative vision and technical complexity"},{"time":555808,"text":"like the Pantheon actually happen?"},{"time":558302,"text":"Someone themselves, perhaps Hadrian,"},{"time":562230,"text":"needed a brilliant creative vision."},{"time":565421,"text":"They also needed the storytelling\nand leadership skills"},{"time":568214,"text":"necessary to fund and execute it,"},{"time":570992,"text":"and a mastery of science and technology"},{"time":573854,"text":"with the ability and knowhow"},{"time":575937,"text":"to push existing innovations even farther."},{"time":579983,"text":"It is my belief that to create\nthese rare game changers"},{"time":583903,"text":"requires you to pull off at least five miracles."},{"time":588033,"text":"The problem is, no matter how talented,"},{"time":590726,"text":"rich or smart you are,"},{"time":592458,"text":"you only get one to one and a half miracles."},{"time":595484,"text":"That's it. That's the quota."},{"time":597266,"text":"Then you run out of time, money, enthusiasm,"},{"time":599879,"text":"whatever."},{"time":601258,"text":"Remember, most people can't even imagine"},{"time":603535,"text":"one of these technical miracles,"},{"time":605442,"text":"and you need at least five to make a Pantheon."},{"time":608551,"text":"In my experience, these rare visionaries"},{"time":611052,"text":"who can think across the worlds of art,"},{"time":612889,"text":"design and engineering"},{"time":614716,"text":"have the ability to notice"},{"time":616918,"text":"when others have provided enough of the miracles"},{"time":619635,"text":"to bring the goal within reach."},{"time":622191,"text":"Driven by the clarity of their vision,"},{"time":624828,"text":"they summon the courage and determination"},{"time":627138,"text":"to deliver the remaining miracles"},{"time":629235,"text":"and they often take what other people think to be"},{"time":632785,"text":"insurmountable obstacles"},{"time":634831,"text":"and turn them into features."},{"time":636616,"text":"Take the oculus of the Pantheon."},{"time":639543,"text":"By insisting that it be in the design,"},{"time":641441,"text":"it meant you couldn't use much\nof the structural technology"},{"time":644314,"text":"that had been developed for Roman arches."},{"time":647288,"text":"However, by instead embracing it"},{"time":650186,"text":"and rethinking weight and stress distribution,"},{"time":652774,"text":"they came up with a design that only works"},{"time":655256,"text":"if there's a big hole in the roof."},{"time":657160,"text":"That done, you now get the aesthetic"},{"time":660167,"text":"and design benefits of light, cooling"},{"time":664548,"text":"and that critical direct connection with the heavens."},{"time":667848,"text":"Not bad."},{"time":669892,"text":"These people not only believed"},{"time":671953,"text":"that the impossible can be done,"},{"time":674009,"text":"but that it must be done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":676835,"text":"Enough ancient history."},{"time":678936,"text":"What are some recent examples of innovations"},{"time":682069,"text":"that combine creative design"},{"time":683948,"text":"and technological advances in a way so profound"},{"time":687191,"text":"that they will be remembered"},{"time":688520,"text":"a thousand years from now?"},{"time":690353,"text":"Well, putting a man on the moon was a good one,"},{"time":693449,"text":"and returning him safely to Earth wasn't bad either."},{"time":696466,"text":"Talk about one giant leap:"},{"time":698958,"text":"It's hard to imagine a more profound moment"},{"time":701406,"text":"in human history"},{"time":702718,"text":"than when we first left our world"},{"time":704891,"text":"to set foot on another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706782,"text":"So what came after the moon?"},{"time":709003,"text":"One is tempted to say that today's pantheon"},{"time":711811,"text":"is the Internet,"},{"time":713472,"text":"but I actually think that's quite wrong,"},{"time":715941,"text":"or at least it's only part of the story."},{"time":718796,"text":"The Internet isn't a Pantheon."},{"time":721312,"text":"It's more like the invention of concrete:"},{"time":723903,"text":"important, absolutely necessary"},{"time":726478,"text":"to build the Pantheon,"},{"time":727918,"text":"and enduring,"},{"time":729274,"text":"but entirely insufficient by itself."},{"time":732465,"text":"However, just as the technology of concrete"},{"time":735397,"text":"was critical in realization of the Pantheon,"},{"time":738984,"text":"new designers will use the\ntechnologies of the Internet"},{"time":742199,"text":"to create novel concepts that will endure."},{"time":745397,"text":"The smartphone is a perfect example."},{"time":747455,"text":"Soon the majority of people on the planet"},{"time":749200,"text":"will have one,"},{"time":750534,"text":"and the idea of connecting everyone"},{"time":752935,"text":"to both knowledge and each other will endure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756185,"text":"So what's next?"},{"time":757493,"text":"What imminent advance will be\nthe equivalent of the Pantheon?"},{"time":760899,"text":"Thinking about this,"},{"time":762334,"text":"I rejected many very plausible"},{"time":764881,"text":"and dramatic breakthroughs to come,"},{"time":766777,"text":"such as curing cancer."},{"time":768794,"text":"Why? Because Pantheons are anchored"},{"time":772132,"text":"in designed physical objects,"},{"time":775067,"text":"ones that inspire by simply seeing"},{"time":777389,"text":"and experiencing them,"},{"time":778809,"text":"and will continue to do so indefinitely."},{"time":781691,"text":"It is a different kind of language, like art."},{"time":786264,"text":"These other vital contributions that extend life"},{"time":789036,"text":"and relieve suffering are, of course, critical,"},{"time":791729,"text":"and fantastic,"},{"time":793416,"text":"but they're part of the continuum of"},{"time":795209,"text":"our overall knowledge and technology,"},{"time":797721,"text":"like the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":800245,"text":"So what is next?"},{"time":802589,"text":"Perhaps counterintuitively,"},{"time":804308,"text":"I'm guessing it's a visionary idea"},{"time":806620,"text":"from the late 1930s"},{"time":808474,"text":"that's been revived every decade since:"},{"time":811634,"text":"autonomous vehicles."},{"time":813648,"text":"Now you're thinking, give me a break."},{"time":815386,"text":"How can a fancy version of cruise control"},{"time":818904,"text":"be profound?"},{"time":820604,"text":"Look, much of our world"},{"time":822728,"text":"has been designed around \nroads and transportation."},{"time":826211,"text":"These were as essential to the success"},{"time":828086,"text":"of the Roman Empire"},{"time":829584,"text":"as the interstate highway system"},{"time":831569,"text":"to the prosperity and development"},{"time":833363,"text":"of the United States."},{"time":835573,"text":"Today, these roads that interconnect our world"},{"time":838607,"text":"are dominated by cars and trucks"},{"time":840705,"text":"that have remained largely unchanged"},{"time":842573,"text":"for 100 years."},{"time":845144,"text":"Although perhaps not obvious today,"},{"time":848403,"text":"autonomous vehicles will be the key technology"},{"time":852988,"text":"that enables us to redesign our cities"},{"time":856086,"text":"and, by extension, civilization."},{"time":858305,"text":"Here's why:"},{"time":859907,"text":"Once they become ubiquitous,"},{"time":861660,"text":"each year, these vehicles will save"},{"time":864197,"text":"tens of thousands of lives in the United States alone"},{"time":867305,"text":"and a million globally."},{"time":870432,"text":"Automotive energy consumption and air pollution"},{"time":873331,"text":"will be cut dramatically."},{"time":875704,"text":"Much of the road congestion"},{"time":877109,"text":"in and out of our cities will disappear."},{"time":880919,"text":"They will enable compelling new concepts"},{"time":883606,"text":"in how we design cities, work,"},{"time":886075,"text":"and the way we live."},{"time":888012,"text":"We will get where we're going faster"},{"time":890558,"text":"and society will recapture vast amounts"},{"time":893556,"text":"of lost productivity"},{"time":894847,"text":"now spent sitting in traffic basically polluting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898488,"text":"But why now? Why do we think this is ready?"},{"time":901761,"text":"Because over the last 30 years,"},{"time":903955,"text":"people from outside the automotive industry"},{"time":906003,"text":"have spent countless billions"},{"time":908111,"text":"creating the needed miracles,"},{"time":909846,"text":"but for entirely different purposes."},{"time":912718,"text":"It took folks like DARPA, universities,"},{"time":915346,"text":"and companies completely\noutside of the automotive industry"},{"time":918510,"text":"to notice that if you were clever about it,"},{"time":920811,"text":"autonomy could be done now."},{"time":923341,"text":"So what are the five miracles\nneeded for autonomous vehicles?"},{"time":926724,"text":"One, you need to know"},{"time":928367,"text":"where you are and exactly what time it is."},{"time":931101,"text":"This was solved neatly by the GPS system,"},{"time":933509,"text":"Global Positioning System,"},{"time":934821,"text":"that the U.S. Government put in place."},{"time":937487,"text":"You need to know where all the roads are,"},{"time":940010,"text":"what the rules are, and where you're going."},{"time":942913,"text":"The various needs of personal navigation systems,"},{"time":945496,"text":"in-car navigation systems,"},{"time":947251,"text":"and web-based maps address this."},{"time":950284,"text":"You must have near-continuous communication"},{"time":952911,"text":"with high-performance computing networks"},{"time":954804,"text":"and with others nearby"},{"time":956474,"text":"to understand their intent."},{"time":959789,"text":"The wireless technologies\ndeveloped for mobile devices,"},{"time":962897,"text":"with some minor modifications,"},{"time":964690,"text":"are completely suitable to solve this."},{"time":967649,"text":"You'll probably want some restricted roadways"},{"time":970139,"text":"to get started"},{"time":971329,"text":"that both society and its lawyers"},{"time":973807,"text":"agree are safe to use for this."},{"time":975679,"text":"This will start with the HOV lanes"},{"time":977528,"text":"and move from there."},{"time":979661,"text":"But finally, you need to recognize"},{"time":982212,"text":"people, signs and objects."},{"time":984315,"text":"Machine vision, special sensors,\nand high-performance computing"},{"time":987369,"text":"can do a lot of this,"},{"time":988941,"text":"but it turns out a lot is not good enough"},{"time":991499,"text":"when your family is on board."},{"time":993440,"text":"Occasionally, humans will \nneed to do sense-making."},{"time":996961,"text":"For this, you might actually have to wake up"},{"time":1000573,"text":"your passenger and ask them what the hell"},{"time":1002669,"text":"that big lump is in the middle of the road."},{"time":1005487,"text":"Not so bad, and it will give us a sense of purpose"},{"time":1007831,"text":"in this new world."},{"time":1009684,"text":"Besides, once the first drivers explain"},{"time":1012424,"text":"to their confused car"},{"time":1013750,"text":"that the giant chicken at the fork in the road"},{"time":1016416,"text":"is actually a restaurant,"},{"time":1017959,"text":"and it's okay to keep driving,"},{"time":1020263,"text":"every other car on the surface of the Earth"},{"time":1023683,"text":"will know that from that point on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1026605,"text":"Five miracles, mostly delivered,"},{"time":1028868,"text":"and now you just need a clear vision"},{"time":1030746,"text":"of a better world filled with autonomous vehicles"},{"time":1033583,"text":"with seductively beautiful \nand new functional designs"},{"time":1037196,"text":"plus a lot of money and hard work"},{"time":1039650,"text":"to bring it home."},{"time":1041246,"text":"The beginning is now only a handful of years away,"},{"time":1044268,"text":"and I predict that autonomous vehicles"},{"time":1046136,"text":"will permanently change our world"},{"time":1048207,"text":"over the next several decades."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052391,"text":"In conclusion, I've come to believe"},{"time":1055043,"text":"that the ingredients for the next Pantheons"},{"time":1057281,"text":"are all around us,"},{"time":1058668,"text":"just waiting for visionary people"},{"time":1060855,"text":"with the broad knowledge,"},{"time":1062589,"text":"multidisciplinary skills,"},{"time":1064199,"text":"and intense passion"},{"time":1066067,"text":"to harness them to make their dreams a reality."},{"time":1071153,"text":"But these people don't spontaneously"},{"time":1073649,"text":"pop into existence."},{"time":1074988,"text":"They need to be nurtured and encouraged"},{"time":1076827,"text":"from when they're little kids."},{"time":1078606,"text":"We need to love them and help them"},{"time":1080466,"text":"discover their passions."},{"time":1082185,"text":"We need to encourage them to work hard"},{"time":1084399,"text":"and help them understand that failure"},{"time":1086836,"text":"is a necessary ingredient for success,"},{"time":1089707,"text":"as is perseverance."},{"time":1091888,"text":"We need to help them to find their own role models,"},{"time":1094986,"text":"and give them the confidence\nto believe in themselves"},{"time":1097658,"text":"and to believe that anything is possible,"},{"time":1100435,"text":"and just as my grandpa did when\nhe took me shopping for surplus,"},{"time":1103944,"text":"and just as my parents did"},{"time":1105727,"text":"when they took me to science museums,"},{"time":1107749,"text":"we need to encourage them to find their own path,"},{"time":1111030,"text":"even if it's very different from our own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1113687,"text":"But a cautionary note:"},{"time":1115095,"text":"We also need to periodically pry them away"},{"time":1117529,"text":"from their modern miracles,"},{"time":1118998,"text":"the computers, phones, tablets,"},{"time":1120969,"text":"game machines and TVs,"},{"time":1122563,"text":"take them out into the sunlight"},{"time":1124807,"text":"so they can experience both the natural"},{"time":1126936,"text":"and design wonders of our world,"},{"time":1129833,"text":"our planet and our civilization."},{"time":1132075,"text":"If we don't, they won't understand"},{"time":1135002,"text":"what these precious things are"},{"time":1136884,"text":"that someday they will be resopnsible"},{"time":1139479,"text":"for protecting and improving."},{"time":1141761,"text":"We also need them to understand"},{"time":1143404,"text":"something that doesn't seem adequately appreciated"},{"time":1146433,"text":"in our increasingly tech-dependent world,"},{"time":1148896,"text":"that art and design"},{"time":1150579,"text":"are not luxuries,"},{"time":1152492,"text":"nor somehow incompatible"},{"time":1154318,"text":"with science and engineering."},{"time":1156187,"text":"They are in fact essential to what makes us special."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1161762,"text":"Someday, if you get the chance,"},{"time":1164277,"text":"perhaps you can take your kids"},{"time":1165814,"text":"to the actual Pantheon,"},{"time":1167585,"text":"as we will our daughter Kira,"},{"time":1170245,"text":"to experience firsthand"},{"time":1172323,"text":"the power of that astonishing design,"},{"time":1176580,"text":"which on one otherwise unremarkable day in Rome,"},{"time":1180324,"text":"reached 2,000 years into the future"},{"time":1183351,"text":"to set the course for my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1186009,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1188140,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}